     2| * WallpaperWaifu live wallpaper downloader
     3| *
     4| * Default behavior:
     5| *   Download the newest listing page from https://wallpaperwaifu.com/.
     6| *   Videos are saved to project-folder\downloads.
     7| *   History is saved separately from the MoeWalls script.
     8| *
     9| * Common commands:
    10| *   node .\scripts\download-wallpaperwaifu-first-page.mjs
    11| *   node .\scripts\download-wallpaperwaifu-first-page.mjs --page 2
    12| *   node .\scripts\download-wallpaperwaifu-first-page.mjs --out "D:\Wallpapers\WallpaperWaifu"
    13| *   node .\scripts\download-wallpaperwaifu-first-page.mjs --dry-run
    14| */
